Archived projet: This project is no longer under active development and was archived on 2024-07-24.

General layout of the rMake tree:

build           Trove build implementation, including client, dispatcher, and worker bits
cmdline         Command-line entry point for trove job interface
core            Core job functionality, including the dispatcher
lib             Utility modules and extensions for third-party libs
messagebus      Message bus client implementation and message type definitions
worker          Task-running component used on worker nodes
